OL,3,CGareth Bale part of rejected group bid
OL,4,Cto buy Cardiff City
OL,6,FEarlier this week the US consortium
OL,7,Fwas also linked with a takeover of
OL,8,FPlymouth Argyle.
OL,10,FBale retired from football in January
OL,11,F2023 at the age of 33. He won five
OL,12,FChampions League titles with Real and
OL,13,Fis the men's all-time record
OL,14,Fgoalscorer for Wales with 41 in 111
OL,15,Fcaps.
OL,17,FHe was linked with an emotional move
OL,18,Fto Cardiff, his hometown club, after
OL,19,Fleaving Madrid in 2022 but instead
OL,20,Fjoined MLS side LAFC.
